    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This beauty is in truly spectacular shape\u2014practically flawless inside and out! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and still has that 'brand new' feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered its whole life, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
